Package com.edit.reach.fragments

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MapFragment.OnMapInteractionListener
    This interface must be implemented by activities that contain this fragment to allow an interaction in this fragment to be communicated to the activity and potentially other fragments contained in that activity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControlFragment
    This fragment is used for when the vehicle is moving.
    MapFragment
    This fragment displays a map.
    MilestonesFragment
    This fragment allows the user to add milestones to a chosen route in the stationary mode.
    RouteFragment
    This fragment is used when vehicle is standing still.
    SuggestionFragment
    When a button has been clicked in the controlfragment this fragment gives the user a way to choose a milestone.
